name: eTimeMachine.com Inc
tag_list: software, timesheet, time, expense, attendance, project-management, resource-management
overview:
eTimeMachine is a software development company with unique expertise in Enterprise Work Management software application and implementation. It focuses on providing custom enterprise work management solutions that best meet today’s fast paced companies and understands the ever-changing demands constantly being placed on organizations, their project managers, and teams.

eTimeMachine has extensive experience in delivering enterprise project management software solutions that have been successfully implemented across a broad range of industries including Transportation, Pharmaceutical, Energy, Automotive, Financial Investment, Defense, Manufacturing, Research and Development.
